<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .header {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .important {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-left: 4px solid #6c757d;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to PostcardMailer.us!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <p>Hello <%= @user.email %>,</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for signing up with PostcardMailer.us. We're excited to have you on board!</p>
    
    <div class="important">
      <p><strong>Important:</strong> Your account requires manual verification before you can send postcards. This helps us maintain the quality of our service and prevent misuse.</p>
      
      <p>We'll review your account shortly and send you a verification confirmation email once approved.</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>In the meantime, you can set up your address book and explore the features available in your account.</p>
    
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please reply to this email.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© <%= Date.today.year %> PostcardMailer.us</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
